This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing (NLP) techniques for summarizing Electronic Health Records (EHRs). Additionally, the paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms, which makes it relevant to the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CY (Computers and Society). Finally, the paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which makes it relevant to the sub-category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
